name: Python-stardict
body:
# python-stardict

Python module reading the StarDict dictionaries.

This is just a trivial project and developed mainly for fun,
but it may offer some help if you want do some work on Stardict dictionaries.

Feel free to use it, and please let me know if it helps you a bit :-)
tagline: python module reading the StarDict dictionaries
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
